\omega(n)=\sum_{p|n}1,
\sum_{\begin{array}{c} n\leq x\\ n\equiv a\ (q) \end{array}}\omega(n).
\sum_{\begin{array}{c} n\leq x\\ n\equiv a\ (q) \end{array}}\sum_{p|n}1=\sum_{p\leq x}\sum_{\begin{array}{c} n\leq x,\ p|n\\ n\equiv a\ (q) \end{array}}1.
\sum_{\begin{array}{c} p\leq x\\ p\nmid q \end{array}}\sum_{\begin{array}{c} n\leq\frac{x}{p}\\ n\equiv p^{-1}a\ (q) \end{array}}1=\sum_{\begin{array}{c} p\leq x\\ p\nmid q \end{array}}\left(\frac{x}{pq}+O(1)\right) 
